8 A Lyga#Team of the Year|2018]]<ref>{{cite web |title=A Lygos Rinktin\u0117 2018 Sezono |url=https://www.facebook.com/Alyga.LT/photos/a.105011302040/10155564631957041/?type=3 |website=Facebook |publisher=A Lyga |accessdate=17 November 2018 |language=Lithuanian |date=17 November 2018}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20110813135106/http://redbulls.com/soccer/salzburg/de/Daniel-Offenbacher.html Players profile Homepage FC Red Bull Salzburg]\n\n{{FK S\u016bduva Marijampol\u0117 squad}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Offenbacher, Daniel}}\n[[Category:1992 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from Murau District]]\n[[Category:Austrian footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:Austria youth international footballers]]\n[[Category:Austria under-21 international footballers]]\n[[Category:FC Red Bull Salzburg players]]\n[[Category:FC Blau-Wei\u00df Linz players]]\n[[Category:SC Wiener Neustadt players]]\n[[Category:SK Sturm Graz players]]\n[[Category:Wolfsberger AC players]]\n[[Category:FK S\u016bduva Marijampol\u0117 players]]\n[[Category:FC Hermannstadt players]]\n[[Category:Austrian Football Bundesliga players]]\n[[Category:Austrian Regionalliga players]]\n[[Category:A Lyga players]]\n[[Category:Liga I players]]\n[[Category:Austrian expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Lithuania]]\n[[Category:Austrian expatriate sportspeople in Lithuania]]\n[[Category:Austrian expatriate sportspeople in Romania]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Romania]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Styria]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox football biography\n| name = Daniel Offenbacher\n| image = SV Mattersburg vs. SK Sturm Graz 2015-09-13 (031).jpg\n| fullname = \n| height = {{height|m=1.75}}\n| birth_date = {{Birth date and age|1992|2|18}}\n| birth_place = [[Scheifling]], [[Austria]]\n| currentclub  = [[FK S\u016bduva|S\u016bduva]] \n| clubnumber = 92\n| position = [[Midfielder]]\n